Test Case 5: Add Item for Sale
Test Case ID: TC_ADD_ITEM_01
Description: Test adding a new item for sale.
Preconditions: User must be logged in.

Steps:
Open the "Add Item" page in user page.
Enter valid information in all required fields (title, description, price, size, condition, category).
Upload an image of the item.
Click on the "Add Item" button.
Expected Result:
The item is added successfully and appears in the user's items for sale.
A success message "Item added successfully" is displayed.
Actual Result:
The item is added successfully and appears in the user's items for sale.
A success message "Item added successfully" is displayed.